<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_05_SU_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema514_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_05_su_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">              
              <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>7</span><span>8</span></span
              >과<span class="fraction_box"><span>5</span><span>12</span></span
              >를 통분하는 방법을 알아봅시다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                  <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>7</span><span>8</span></span
                  >과<span class="fraction_box"><span>5</span><span>12</span></span
                  >를 통분하려면 어떤 수를 공통분모로 나타낼 수 있을지 이야기해 보세요.
                </div>
              </div>              
            </h3>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">두 분모의 곱이나 최소공배수로 나타낼 수 있습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">두 분모의 곱을 공통분모로 하여 통분해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="fraction_row">
                <div class="fra_ex fra_arr">
                  <div class="fra_parens">
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>7</span><span>8</span></span
                    >,
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>5</span><span>12</span></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fra_inn fra_arr">
                  <div class="fra_parens">
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                      <span>7&times;12</span>
                      <span>
                        <span>8&times;</span>
                        <span class="input_wrap answer2">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field>
                        </span>
                      </span> </span
                    >,
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                      <span>
                        <span>5&times;</span>
                        <span class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field>
                        </span>
                      </span>
                      <span>12&times;8</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fra_inn">
                  <div class="fra_parens">
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(84)/(96)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    ,
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(40)/(96)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">두 분모의 최소공배수를 공통분모로 하여 통분해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="fraction_row">
                <div class="fra_ex fra_arr">
                  <div class="fra_parens">
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>7</span><span>8</span></span>,
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>5</span><span>12</span></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fra_inn fra_arr">
                  <div class="fra_parens">
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                      <span>
                        <span>7&times;</span>
                        <span class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                        </span>
                      </span>
                      <span>8&times;3</span>
                    </span>
                    ,
                    <span class="fraction_box f32b">
                      <span>5&times;2</span>
                      <span>
                        <span>12&times;</span>
                        <span class="input_wrap answer2">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                        </span>
                      </span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fra_inn">
                  <div class="fra_parens">
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(21)/(24)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    ,
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(84)/(96)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <article class="page page_4">
          <h3 lang="y">앞의 두 방법을 비교하여 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="input_wrap">
            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
            <div class="example_box">
              <p lang="y">두 분모의 곱을 공통분모로 하여 통분하면 최소공배수를 구하지 않아도 되고, 두 분모의 최소공배수를 공통분모로 하여 통분 하면 분모와 분자의 수가 작아져서 계산이 간단합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
